data.meta_description:
8 likes, 1 comments - aperfectspace on October 31, 2023: "Newest Listing - Stallion, Alison, NSW, Australia

Set on 60 acres, this idyllic rural horse farm is just one hour north of Sydney.

A tree lined driveway takes you to the main house which features two large living areas plus pool room and separate dining room with double sided fireplace. Accommodation includes two loft style bedrooms in the main house and a detached cottage overlooking the pool offering a further 3 double bedrooms making a total of 5 bedrooms all with ensuites. In addition, the home features a powder room. Boasting an entertainers kitchen with stone bench top, an outdoor bbq area where you can overlook the pool and enjoy spectacular sunsets and a basement man cave with a golf simulator. The property has stables and extensive paddocks as well as a horse walker and dam. Additionally, there is ample onsite parking available.

Boasting an array of contemporary, yet rustic features, this property offers so many options for stills, TVCs and film.".
